@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<div class="text-center mb-5">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to MellonBank</h1>
    <p class="lead">Your trusted partner for digital banking and financial management.</p>
</div>

<div class="row mb-4">
    <div class="col-12">
        <h2>About MellonBank</h2>
        <p>
            MellonBank is an e-banking platform that provides secure account management for customers
            and a comprehensive administration portal for bank staff. Whether you are managing your
            personal accounts or overseeing the operations of the entire branch, MellonBank offers
            the tools you need to get the job done.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<hr />

<div class="row mb-4">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>For Customers</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>View Your Accounts</strong> — See all your accounts at a glance.</li>
            <li><strong>Check Balance</strong> — View balances in both EUR and USD with live exchange rates.</li>
            <li><strong>Deposit Funds</strong> — Add money to your own account.</li>
            <li><strong>Transfer Funds</strong> — Send money to third-party accounts with real-time balance validation.</li>
            <li><strong>Account Details</strong> — Review your account number, branch, and type.</li>
            <li><strong>Change Password</strong> — Update your security credentials at any time.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>For Staff</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Manage Customers</strong> — Add, edit, or remove customer records by AFM.</li>
            <li><strong>Manage Accounts</strong> — Create and maintain bank accounts for customers by account number.</li>
            <li><strong>Search Customers</strong> — Quickly find any customer by their AFM.</li>
            <li><strong>View All Customers</strong> — Browse the full list of registered clients.</li>
            <li><strong>Full CRUD Access</strong> — Complete control over customer and account data.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

<hr />

<div class="row mb-4">
    <div class="col-12">
        <h3>Public API</h3>
        <p>
            MellonBank also exposes a public API that provides the latest exchange rates used by the bank.
            Any user, authenticated or not, can query this endpoint to retrieve conversion rates for EUR
            to Australian Dollar, Swiss Franc, British Pound, and US Dollar.
        </p>
        <p>
            <a asp-controller="Currency" asp-action="GetRates" class="btn btn-outline-primary">View Exchange Rates (JSON)</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<hr />

<div class="row mb-4">
    <div class="col-12">
        <h3>Security &amp; Authentication</h3>
        <p>
            MellonBank uses ASP.NET Core Identity for secure authentication and role-based authorization.
            Customer and Staff accounts are strictly separated, with each role accessing only the
            functionality appropriate to their position. All sensitive operations require authentication,
            and user passwords are never stored in plain text.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
